step.tex:
\text{A function is increasing if }\\
\quad f(x) > f(y), x\gt y\implies \frac{d}{dx}f(x) \gt 0\\
\text{As }\frac{d}{dx}f(x)\gt 0,f(x)\text{ is strictly increasing.}

\text{A function is increasing if }\\
\quad f(x) > f(y), x\lt y\implies \frac{d}{dx}f(x)\lt 0\\
\text{As }\frac{d}{dx}f(x)\nless 0,f(x)\text{ is not increasing.}
